{"tid":1123587,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[怕左煙仔何?] 笑X死 吸煙與健康委員會 原來仲未搵到IQOS禍害","createTime":"2019-04-24T14:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T23:30:25.000Z","uid":54373,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5bf35cec22b147073bb140bca4ddab9fb5e598b8","tid":1123587,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T14:10:58.000Z","msg":"真煙禍害 &nbsp;(好長,乜癌都有,按入link睇)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.smokefree.hk/tc/content/web.do?page=ActiveSmoking\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smokefree.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontent%2Fweb.do%3Fpage%3DActiveSmoking&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0qwVmkNCIo3TbJkxuaymrXU%3D&h=45e48348\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.smokefree.hk/tc/content/web.do?page=ActiveSmoking</a><br />\n=====================<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加熱非燃燒煙草製品<br />\n 對身體的影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.smokefree.hk/tc/content/web.do?page=hnbtp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smokefree.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontent%2Fweb.do%3Fpage%3Dhnbtp&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0qwVmkNCIo3TbJkxuaymrXU%3D&h=6e31e4d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.smokefree.hk/tc/content/web.do?page=hnbtp</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">    煙草商聲稱加熱非燃燒煙草製品釋出的化學物較傳統捲煙少，可減少對身體的危害，委員會認為這是宣傳技倆，意圖淡化吸煙對身體帶來的傷害。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"> (屌你! 有證據咪講囉!)</span><br />\n<br />\n    現時有關加熱非燃燒煙草製品的研究不多。但任何煙草產品對身體健康的長期影響不容忽視，切莫隨便嘗試。 (講乜撚廢話?)<br />\n<br />\n    世界衞生組織表示所有形式的煙草使用都有害，煙草本身具有毒性，即使是天然形式也含致癌物質。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"> (又係無證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span><br />\n<br />\n    部分有毒或致癌物質是沒有安全水平的，危害巿民健康。<br />\n    目前還<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有證據表明</span>減少對煙草化學物質的暴露會降低人類的健康風險，以及二手物質的潛在影響。<br />\n<br />\n    歐洲有研究發現，加熱非燃燒煙草製品同樣含有捲煙中常見的尼古丁、揮發性有機化合物、一氧化碳及致癌物多環芳香烴等。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"> (唔敢講個份量<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span></span>"},{"pid":"94a7afdd0dada5fa7e66b56562d194097681adc8","tid":1123587,"uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T14:13:14.000Z","msg":"我查不出這人有什麼罪來(路加福音23章1-12節)"},{"pid":"a0c00b94e6483a2d7f25373f7cdf124cc8d42ad8","tid":1123587,"uid":9710,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"還我iqos 還我ploom"},{"pid":"f8a7a42630daf41581531ba2d5b90e41e7d57407","tid":1123587,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:37:08.000Z","msg":"alex做到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2197782fc9ac046b0c7054fd80852ef7ab8cab3c","tid":1123587,"uid":26168,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:17:22.000Z","msg":"佢越講得多乜撚嘢煙草產品禍害就越on9,咁撚禍害咪全面禁煙囉，講鳩咩"},{"pid":"99ed83cef94e6245d8bb069628b1200c85bdff45","tid":1123587,"uid":86793,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:23:39.000Z","msg":"根本全世界都推廣緊 係政府冇稅收就抺黑電子煙 利申非煙民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472ec17ec0a567ce882aa4a0bccf23b788328029","tid":1123587,"uid":90521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"99ed83cef94e6245d8bb069628b1200c85bdff45","tid":1123587,"uid":86793,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:23:39.000Z","msg":"根本全世界都推廣緊 係政府冇稅收就抺黑電子煙 利申非煙民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:29:30.000Z","msg":"其實冇煙民反對加熱煙收稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2bcc09926ba36ea803ad56a42db7472d24ce3d","tid":1123587,"uid":16756,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:44:54.000Z","msg":"$38稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im